<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>His sister Gigi Hadid revealed she is a new mum after welcoming a baby girl over the weekend.</p>

<p>And while Gigi and her boyfriend Zayn Malik spend time with their newborn at the family farm in Pennsylvania, Anwar Hadid is not far away in New York City.</p>

